It appears you are using integrated <span class="abbreviation">PID<template class="tooltiptext" data-text="Proportional Integral Derivative"></template></span> on your SparkMaxes. Instead of using TrapizoidProfile, which runs on the roboRIO, you need to use the integrated version. Simply call m_pidController.setReference(m_goal, SparkBase.ControlType.kMAXMotionPositionControl). You will need to change your m_goal to a double or float for this to work.<br>
